about.summary: Conda environment and package access extension from within Jupyter

name: nbexamples
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}
{% set gh_org = "danielballan" %}
{% set gh_repo = "nbexamples" %}

package:
  name: {{ gh_repo }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ gh_repo }}-v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f391b42ea6856d92a06fafa18ede464e400c9b2804a2a022d0b7197fd4bd4061

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - notebook >=4.2.0
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - nbconvert
    - nbformat
    - notebook >=4.2.0
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - nbexamples

about:
  home: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  summary: Conda environment and package access extension from within Jupyter

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - danielballan
    - ericdill
    - mariusvniekerk
    - parente
